{"tid":1576602,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"新運動發起 經過太子站大叫","createTime":"2019-09-17T10:12:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T10:37:37.000Z","uid":288058,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e8fcf75356aa91a2736efedc6977aabac8247dde","tid":1576602,"uid":288058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T10:12:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">突發其想，不如每次經過太子站<br />\n就對著外面大叫「交出CCTV」「光復香港」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">首先突然一下可以嚇到身有屎嘅黨鐵職員<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n久而久之可以令到佢哋一聽到有人嗌就驚<br />\n<br />\n其次呢個做法唔使定時，隨時隨地都可以進行<br />\n唔會夜晚嘈到人，唔會有任何被捕嘅風險<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n覺得怕羞嘅巴絲可以搭港鐵嗰陣同朋友一齊嗌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">各位巴絲覺得可唔可行呢</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[size=6]光復香港 世代革命[/size=4]"},{"pid":"6e42dff537393119a25eaf8d3d779d795be68e58","tid":1576602,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T10:12:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yt2HG33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyt2HG33.jpg&h=9fcb0aae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TrPZKfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrPZKfU.jpg&h=433e1fe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【922攻略流出】<br />\n907<span style=\"color: gold;\">加強版</span>配合hkmap live <br />\n更「大局」交通測試，彩虹戰衣、影帝、機巴、塞鐵、嶄新突擊RB、私家車傾巢而出，裡應外合 <br />\n+機場員工集體Call Sick <br />\n+雷達站/機場附近新搞作<br />\n+大量中港貨櫃司機加入物資支援！<br />\n<br />\n更多攻略，陸續公布，敬請留意"},{"pid":"7bcdf3c639aad76ff0744c9eea7717e71cda3321","tid":1576602,"uid":288058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T10:13:19.000Z","msg":"嚇死班黨鐵高層"},{"pid":"bffdc78e91dfc47dd46b17271a4f05fe466e57ad","tid":1576602,"uid":1780